    <unit id="1757977b-ae12-47dc-981a-f051e1b92412">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 2</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: # </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>GoldWave</source>
        <target>GoldWave 支持插件</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="8b8e4caf-5d20-48c4-9d8f-c2d0fc7e4442">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 4</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Authors: Joseph Lee, Day Garwood, NVDA contributors.</source>
        <target>作者：Joseph Lee、Day Garwood 及 NVDA 贡献者。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="a0aaa0d8-b7bc-42cb-a8c9-13e9bc936a4f">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 6</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>This app module enhances access and usage of GoldWave audio editor.</source>
        <target>此插件可增强 GoldWave 音频编辑器的无障碍访问与使用体验。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="87bcc57a-4963-49d1-bb28-76fe69363cd8">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 8</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: ## </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Shortcuts</source>
        <target>快捷键 ##</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="62a73e7f-595c-47e2-bfdb-b43c24941a24">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 10</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>All commands support speech on demand mode.</source>
        <target>所有命令均支持手动朗读模式。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="d2b61c62-bcc3-4ba7-84c2-1c7aff6cc017">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 12</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Control+Shift+P: Announces current track position.</source>
        <target>Control+Shift+P：读出当前音轨位置。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="09ab6954-0f14-45a1-a84a-887ab53f915b">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 13</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>NVDA+Shift+R: Announces remaining time for the currently editing track.</source>
        <target>NVDA+Shift+R：读出当前编辑音轨的剩余时间。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="714df0e7-364f-4809-91d0-17f6f0b3dc31">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 14</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Control+NVDA+1: Announces the channel you are editing.</source>
        <target>Control+NVDA+1：读出正在编辑的声道。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="27e4b3b6-9915-469a-865a-3fefde650052">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 15</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Control+NVDA+2: Announces the total length of the audio file.</source>
        <target>Control+NVDA+2：读出音频文件的总时长。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="13ac6852-6417-4690-82ae-90865dd9bc8a">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 16</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Control+NVDA+3: announces a summary on audio selection information.</source>
        <target>Control+NVDA+3：读出音频选择信息的摘要。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="2b7204df-d759-4915-91d1-6a5e612c1adc">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 17</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Control+NVDA+4: Announces the zoom level.</source>
        <target>Control+NVDA+4：读出缩放级别。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="0856bfcb-9fd8-470c-8435-db80afb87a3e">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 19</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>For more information about GoldWave and keyboard commands, refer to GoldWave Manual.</source>
        <target>有关 GoldWave 及其键盘命令的更多信息，请参阅 GoldWave 使用手册。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="6d2deafa-484b-4c37-b7e6-48dddf94c2d9">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 21</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Note: GoldWave 6 or later and Windows 10 or 11 are required.</source>
        <target>注意：需要 GoldWave 6 或更高版本及 Windows 10 或更高版本系统。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="4c30c718-0691-4c57-baa3-33f9d7147233">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 23</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>For a list of changes made between each add-on releases, refer to [changelogs for add-on releases][1] document.</source>
        <target>有关每个插件版本之间所做的更改，请参阅[插件更新日志（英语）][1]文档。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="03aa8054-c947-418c-b6bb-7af9917536fe">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 25</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
